### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = church-uuid-here
@familyId = family-uuid-here
@memberId = member-uuid-here

### Create a new family
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/families
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "The Smiths",
  "headOfHouseId": "{{memberId}}"
}

### List families
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/families

### Get family by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/families/{{familyId}}

### Update family
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/families/{{familyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "The Smith Family Revised"
}

### Add a member to a family
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/families/{{familyId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": "{{memberId}}",
  "familyRole": "Spouse"
}

### Remove a member from a family
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/families/{{familyId}}/members/{{memberId}}
